'''吡啶氢溴酸盐'''是一种化合物，化学式为C<sub>5</sub>H<sub>6</sub>BrN。它可由[[吡啶|吡啶]]和[[氢溴酸|氢溴酸]]反应得到。<ref>魏军波, 赵奔腾, 慈玉印. 吡啶氢溴酸盐合成研究. 山东化工, 2017. 46 (15): 35-38.</ref>它和[[溴化亚砜|溴化亚砜]]反应，得到C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>6</sub>N<sup>+</sup>Br<sub>3</sub><sup>−</sup>，并放出[[二氧化硫|SO<sub>2</sub>]]。<ref>Mundy, B. P. (2001). Thionyl Bromide. Encyclopedia of Reagents for Organic Synthesis. {{doi|10.1002/047084289X.rt098}}</ref>它和[[溴化亚铜|溴化亚铜]]反应，得到(C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>6</sub>N)<sub>3</sub>[Cu<sub>3</sub>Br<sub>6</sub>]。<ref>Zhang, Deng-Qing; Xu, Qing-Feng; Chen, Jin-Xiang; Liu, Quan; Zhu, Yan-Jun; Lang, Jian-Ping. Syntheses and crystal structures of two novel bromocuprate(I) polymers {(PyH)<sub>3</sub>[Cu<sub>3</sub>Br<sub>6</sub>]​}<sub>​∞</sub> and {(γ-​MePyH)​<sub>2</sub>[Cu<sub>2</sub>Br<sub>4</sub>]​}<sub>∞</sub> ([http://en.cnki.com.cn/Article_en/CJFDTotal-WJHX200311015.htm Article]). ''Wuji Huaxue Xuebao'', 2003. 19 (11): 1232-1236.</ref>它可用作[[:d:Q72435584|7-氨基去乙酰氧基头孢烷酸]]（7-ADCA）合成中的催化剂。<ref>方长明. [http://www.cnki.com.cn/Article/CJFDTotal-HNHU199611027.htm 吡啶氢溴酸盐合成工艺研究]. 河南化工, 1996 (11): 43.</ref>

